Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100997,102040}What's up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102665,104125}Try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:48.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105293,108379}Can't you be faster than Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109005,110173}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:51.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111007,111883}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121768,124020}Lassie went too far…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148795,150296}What's up, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152965,155176}Is it our guest while I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157512,158429}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158429,159639}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159639,161766}Is this the big dog yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162016,163309}That's true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163309,164268}What about you Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166437,170066}The road was divided into four\Ndirections, and while I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170066,171275}I was sleepy and I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178074,179200}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179200,181202}We have guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181744,182745}Guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182745,185206}We are not guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185957,187792}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187792,188710}Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191421,193089}Very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193089,196509}Doucho is very sad,\Nhis chest is almost bursting with pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196509,199846}So one of you will come and ease his grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216612,217739}Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219490,220450}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227457,229417}This is my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230126,232420}This is my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233045,235923}His name is Pace! His specialty\Nis moving the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237133,239218}I'm Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239218,241846}By the way, do you know\Na delicious bakery in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241846,243806}Bakery? Maybe that is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243806,246392}I know, Uncle Rice's bakery is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246392,247143}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247143,248144}That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248144,251272}He's helped by his daughter, Mary!\NIt's the best in the whole village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251272,252607}Well I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252607,254609}I have a place to go today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254609,255735}Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263618,264827}We have finally finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264827,267038}Well, let's go for a walk\Nand have a drink together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271083,273336}Oh? Do you still deliver goods at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273503,276422}You work harder than we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287725,289560}John! Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289560,291521}And Lassie? What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309705,311791}Lassie, isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311791,313209}Can you do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322343,323636}And now, next…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324136,327098}We need some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327098,328140}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328558,329433}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329433,331602}This gentle miss, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333312,334397}Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334397,337024}Would your husband be reluctant to look at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337024,338150}I'm rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340987,342655}Stay there and hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344365,345324}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345324,346784}This is the best place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:47.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346784,347952}Come on, Doucho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356669,360298}Ladies and gentlemen, this is\Nthe great partner of the spotlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360298,362758}And this gentle miss,\NI hope you applaud them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365887,366971}And now, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366971,369265}you have the honor to see some of my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369265,371893}We have utensils and all kinds of pans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372184,373936}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379191,380776}Good! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381903,383738}You're welcome, thank you for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383738,385323}I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385448,388993}Rory is doing business and\Nis traveling around England!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388993,390828}Me too I wish I would go to many places!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390828,391412}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391412,393372}My God! My God! My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393372,395666}I would forget something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395666,397043}Please buy me bread to eat at dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397043,398628}Okay! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400338,401672}Let's go! To the bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401672,403549}You are! You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403966,406510}How can you leave your job like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409430,410681}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410681,412391}Today there is no bread because all were sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412391,414602}- Not even one?\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414977,417730}I'll bake a new batch tomorrow morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418064,419982}I understood, there is none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419982,421525}Don't you have bread for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421525,422401}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422401,424487}It's not for me, it is for Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424487,425613}Rory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425613,428240}Yes, that man who has a dog\Nwhich does amazing movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428240,430660}His voice is so loud that\NI can hear him from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430660,434455}He came to this village because I told\Nhim that we have a delicious bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434455,435081}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:15.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435081,435998}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435998,437375}We don't have anything to sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437375,438876}Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:19.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438876,439877}Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439877,442922}But will that man stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:23.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442922,443881}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443881,446842}Tomorrow morning I'll give you fresh bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446842,447385}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449971,450846}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450846,452556}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:37.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453057,457520}Fresh bread makes the hearts of people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457520,459855}Next to that beautiful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459855,462441}Well, I will work tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462441,463776}But what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,465569}You have no house here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465945,468572}Nothing like that, I don't have\Na house at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469365,471450}So, will you sleep in the stable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471617,473703}No no, but I'm a vagabond!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473703,475329}Displacement is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475329,477248}Under the stars of the sky that seem to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477748,480334}Towards that sky to the large galaxies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480334,482336}I sleep under it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482336,483963}Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485089,486716}Sky and stars…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494724,496642}Look like they really fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496642,498519}Somehow this is scary…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498519,499270}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:23.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500438,503065}Have you traveled in many places?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503065,504275}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504608,506277}Just, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:33.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507820,513284}Manchester, Glasgow, Newcastle,\Nand also Liverpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:38.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514744,518247}I only went to the simple villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520124,523169}My father was like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524086,526797}I was used to staying out at night\Nand homeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:52.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526797,532261}but there are many people who are bored\Nto stay between the walls of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:56.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532553,536932}Yet within this dimly lit window is a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:03.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537516,543064}Thinking about it, this is warm and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543064,545191}It seems that staying in a home\Nis a lot more better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546442,550696}But Uncle Rice is always angry\Nand screaming loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551739,552948}It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552948,554825}You should not say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554825,556702}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:19.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559038,559830}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560915,562124}It's Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569423,571759}Can't you smell the delicious things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580101,582103}Pace, it's delicious! It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583145,584271}Oh really? Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584688,586565}Oh really! Really really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587149,589777}But there is a problem with\Nthe handle of this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591028,593280}It can be used again after\Nit has been well repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594156,597284}It seems that Sandy's mother is interested\Nin keeping the dishes well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597701,598327}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598327,599787}This pot is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:00.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600121,600830}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600830,603290}I got it from my deceased grandmother\Nwhen I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603290,605251}That's why I cared about it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605251,608754}Is it you who made this tasty soup…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608754,609547}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610881,613259}Is that right? I apologize for my insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613259,616804}Finally I knew! Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620141,621976}What now are natural people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621976,624478}Haven't you seen a falling star\Nor something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624478,625312}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626397,627106}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627690,628899}It's a falling star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628899,631110}Eh? Where? Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631110,632236}Just gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632236,633571}I saw it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633571,636907}I really saw it! That is the devil… I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644373,645249}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645958,648419}They made a fire in such a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648419,651255}What if a fire starts because of that? Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652047,654008}Now, kids, have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:54.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654008,654842}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654842,655885}Although we enjoy being with you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656760,660764}Don't you have mothers and\Na warm home waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660764,663142}Children have specific times\Nand can't go out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663142,665394}You are not like me, homeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665936,667396}See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667396,669899}Did you have amazing\Nthings for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672234,674486}Doucho wants to make this happen\Nwith greater success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675029,676447}- Bye!\N- Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676447,677406}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677406,678991}Lassie, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681994,685497}That boy owns a huge dog,\Nbeautiful shape, Doucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:26.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686207,686957}It was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707394,708938}I have finished, Doucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708938,709980}Should I sleep now?
Comment: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:58.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:718113,718113}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763993,765077}That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771375,772626}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774420,775504}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775879,777464}It's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777464,779508}Hey! It's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779508,781802}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783929,785931}Oh? A fire started?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785931,787808}It's near my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789435,791562}Water! Water! Curse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795649,796567}Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807077,808329}It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814335,815127}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817171,818088}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818088,819840}I came to deliver the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820341,821467}Hello, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821467,823344}What? Have you brought milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824303,825512}Unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825512,827473}it's not from my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827473,831060}Listen, Mr. Rory needs milk with\Nthe bread at breakfast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831060,832394}Ah, that 's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834021,836940}Lassie, do you want to meet Dousho as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838776,841111}Who came this early morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841945,842946}- Colin?\N- Uh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842946,844239}John! Something bad happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844239,847618}Rory! Rory has troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847618,848869}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863050,864635}How many times should I tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864635,867221}I certainly turned off the fire before I slept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867221,869390}So how it burned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869390,871517}Well, Mr Rice…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872142,874978}This man worked hard to extinguish the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874978,876855}What is important is that the fire\Ndidn't reached the nearby houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876855,879525}What will you do if we can't control the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:43.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880234,883237}I also asked for help without any charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883237,885406}Don't think you will leave safely\Nafter you have caused the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885406,887241}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887699,888826}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,891245}Dad, you always do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891245,894373}You are very interested in your customers\Nto buy bread from our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894373,895707}This guy is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895707,897000}Don't joke with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897000,900170}I bake bread for the villagers only!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900170,903424}I don't sell to men of this kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904258,905175}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905175,906301}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906301,909596}I don't know anything about bread,\Nbut it was hard to extinguish the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909930,911098}This means
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:14.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911098,914101}I must preserve my life and\Nthe life of the people of my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915018,917396}It is better to leave our village immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917980,919231}Do you have an objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921650,922943}I'll tell you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922943,924278}I didn't set fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924278,927281}No, no doubt it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:30.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927281,930993}I understand.  I don't like\Nto say this again though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930993,932119}Scum…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932119,934913}I know that, you don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936331,937416}You see? Definitely the reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941378,943172}I want to say only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:48.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944840,948510}I sell bowls and dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948510,953932}I travel to make people smile through\Nthe acrobatic games that Doucho loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953932,954892}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959271,960355}Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961148,962149}Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962149,964026}I have no other chioce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964443,965611}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965611,967529}Don't say "but" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968113,969406}Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969406,970908}The food was delicious, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973702,975162}It's fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:19.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975162,979791}Well, the store owner wants me\Nto leave, so the village be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980751,982794}We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994765,996767}Rory… left…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998769,1001480}I don't know if the lamp\Nor wood caused th fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001480,1004191}It was close to my house and\Nit almost burned because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:44.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004191,1004942}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005567,1006443}A lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006985,1007986}Or wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007986,1009071}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010322,1011532}Hey Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011532,1013534}To the worst, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014117,1015786}Should I hit the door only?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015786,1016537}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019164,1020916}John, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020916,1021917}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021917,1025045}You say what?  But Mr. Rice is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025045,1026547}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026547,1028340}Mr Rice, I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:13.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028340,1033971}What? I must bake the bread late today\Nwith the oven already cooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033971,1035222}I'll go to bake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035222,1037266}Quick! He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037266,1039101}Sorry, Mr Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039726,1041353}What? I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041353,1043397}Not me, but Colin…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043772,1046149}Excuse me… this, sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046441,1047651}So I said, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050612,1051947}John, tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055951,1057369}Is this the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057369,1058161}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059371,1060455}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060747,1063750}The lamp and firewood were\Nextinguished at 11 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:44.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063959,1064626}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064835,1065586}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:49.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065586,1069006}This means that Colin woke up\Nand looked at the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069006,1071466}How come a child stays up until late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071466,1072342}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072342,1075262}I was trying to see the meteors…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075262,1076555}That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076555,1078181}Falling stars, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078181,1081226}If you talk loudly you will scare the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081226,1082144}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082144,1085480}Anyway, Mr. Rory turned off the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085480,1088609}And extinguished the fire with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088609,1089568}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089568,1090360}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090360,1093322}This means that wasn't the cause of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093322,1094072}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:18.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094740,1098076}If the cause of the fire is different\Nfrom that, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116011,1117804}Enough, just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119473,1121350}Can't you go faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121350,1123310}I'm deaf, you're distracted in driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124478,1125437}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125437,1127856}What do I say to that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127856,1129316}You must apologize to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:53.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129775,1133236}I thought about the safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133236,1134821}If I say so…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134821,1138825}No matter what you say,\Nit's your fault anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:03.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139534,1143080}I was very impressed by Rory's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:03.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143080,1143538}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144164,1146541}I hope he stays in our village\Nand doesn't go anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147250,1148543}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:13.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149002,1153548}I want to talk more with Mr. Rory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163016,1165811}Don't make this sad face, Duocho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:28.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165811,1168772}There are times when people should laugh at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168772,1170982}Hey, aren't you a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190377,1192170}What's up, Pace? Why have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194256,1196675}Hey, get out of the way quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196675,1198635}The ship will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206685,1209229}Here it is! It's Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209229,1210605}Oh! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212399,1214860}Rory will cross the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214860,1217028}Damn, the engine hangs now…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221450,1222576}Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222576,1224119}Wait, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228039,1230667}You too, Dad! Run after the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234129,1235922}Hey Pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236631,1240510}I want to cross this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240510,1243930}In the next village\Nwe will see beautiful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251229,1252606}Hey come on, Pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257694,1258737}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258737,1260197}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260197,1261448}Oh Doucho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:05.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264868,1265827}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265827,1267954}Rory, don't cross this bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268455,1270582}My father, it's my father's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270749,1272584}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272584,1274252}Don't go on that road!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292938,1294022}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294022,1296441}This is because of these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296441,1299528}This means we will do\Nfun things there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303406,1304741}Yeah! Yeah!
